---
title: Easy Creamy Pork & Leek Fusilli with Parmesan Cheese
description: In this dish, we've paired a special seasoning straight from Nan's secret spice drawer with a silky cream-based sauce, then
followed it up with tender pork mince for a 20 minute meal that looks and smells every bit as good as it tastes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easy-creamy-pork-leek-silverbeet-fusilli-b51cc70b.jpg
